        <details class="seo-concept-faq-item" open>
          <summary>How much should I spend on Google Ads?</summary>
          <p>Your budget depends on your market, competition, and sales goals. We usually recommend a minimum budget that allows for enough data to optimize campaigns effectively—usually starting around ₹30k-₹50k per month for smaller markets.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="seo-concept-faq-item">
          <summary>How long does it take to see ROAS results?</summary>
          <p>Google Ads can drive traffic immediately. However, it usually takes 2-4 weeks to gather enough data for initial optimizations and 2-3 months to stabilize and scale a high-performance ROAS engine.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="seo-concept-faq-item">
          <summary>Do you handle both Search and Shopping ads?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We manage the full Google Ads ecosystem, including Search, Shopping, Performance Max, Display, Video (YouTube), and Re-marketing campaigns.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="seo-concept-faq-item">
          <summary>What is included in the monthly management fee?</summary>
          <p>Our fee includes account strategy, campaign setup, daily bid management, ad copy writing, conversion tracking audit, and detailed monthly reporting.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="seo-concept-faq-item">
          <summary>Can you fix my conversion tracking issues?</summary>
          <p>Absolutely. We specialize in setting up Google Tag Manager (GTM), GA4, and server-side tracking to ensure your data is 100% accurate for Google's machine learning bidding.</p>
